aj Helen Sorkmo]] || align=center| 202\n|- \n| align=center|23 || {{flagicon|FIN}} [[Virpi Kuitunen]] || align=center| 188\n|- \n| align=center|24 || {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Jenny Olsson]] || align=center| 187\n|-       \n| align=center|25 || {{flagicon|RUS}} [[Alyona Sidko]] || align=center| 185\n|- \n| align=center|26 || {{flagicon|FIN}} [[Kaisa Varis]] || align=center| 184\n|- \n| align=center|27 || {{flagicon|FIN}} [[Aino-Kaisa Saarinen]] || align=center| 169\n|- \n| align=center|28 || {{flagicon|RUS}} [[Lilia Vasilieva]] || align=center| 163\n|-\n| align=center|29 || {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Elin Ek (cross-country skier)|Elin Ek]] || align=center| 155\n|- \n| align=center|30 || {{flagicon|RUS}} [[Yelena Burukhina]] || align=center| 151\n|}\n{{col-break|width=25%}}\n\n=== Sprint ===\n{| cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border:1px solid #AAAAAA;font-size:86%\" \n|-style=\"background-color: #E4E4E4;\"\n!style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #AAAAAA\" width=10|Rank\n!style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #AAAAAA\" width=200|Skier\n!style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #AAAAAA\" width=50|Points\n|- \n| align=center|'''<span style=\"background-color:red; padding:1px 5px 1px 1px; border-style:solid; border-width:1px; border-color:lightgrey;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>''' || {{flagicon|NOR}} '''[[Marit Bj\u00f8rgen]]''' || align=center| 485\n|- \n| align=center|2 || {{flagicon|NOR}} [[Bente Skari]] || align=center| 410\n|- \n| align=center|3 || {{flagicon|FIN}} [[Pirjo Manninen]] || align=center| 292\n|- \n| align=center|4 || {{flagicon|GER}} [[Manuela Henkel]] || align=center| 276\n|-       \n| align=center|5 || {{flagicon|NOR}} [[Anita Moen]] || align=center| 263\n|- \n| align=center|6 || {{flagicon|NOR}} [[Hilde Gjermundshaug Pedersen]] || align=center| 248\n|- \n| align=center|7 || {{flagicon|GER}} [[Claudia K\u00fcnzel]] || align=center| 230\n|- \n| align=center|8 || {{flagicon|NOR}} [[Maj Helen Sorkmo]] || align=center| 196\n|-\n| align=center|9 || {{flagicon|GER}} [[Evi Sachenbacher]]